Package: cityTripsR
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Exploring and Summarizing City Travel Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Federico", "Gorrini", 
           email = "fgorrini@usf.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    cityTripsR provides simple tools to explore and summarize travel data.
    The package includes functions for calculating trip durations, comparing
    average costs across cities, exploring travel ratings, filtering trips,
    and creating basic travel visualizations. It is designed for analysis and clear documentation.
